e":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T15:29:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/20170524/20031507\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Ffinanceestate%2Fart%2F20170524%2F20031507&d=EkSOzQ7ZVjnG5t8dBASUilKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=997545cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Ffinanceestate%2Fart%2F20170524%2F20031507&h=d5832e8f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/20170524/20031507</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>3日前</strong><br />\n<br />\n另一大行消息說，目前情況與2013年不同，存款超標貸款選擇不多，任何銀行率先加按息等於「自殺」不做生意，倘滙豐加息，中銀「只會多謝」未必跟隨；除非明年港元拆息仍低企，資本成本增加壓力「捱足」一整個年度（今年僅半年影響）後，屆時加按息考慮才較逼切。<br />\n東亞銀行（023）總經理兼個人銀行處主管許文森昨出席新盤定息按揭計劃時表示，提高RWA下限對銀行資金成本帶來壓力，至於會否上調按息，則視乎各方面市況而定。"},{"pid":"e5734eb1c6340c155342b26961a4dba56c4f1305","tid":258976,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T05:23:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/20170524/20031507\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Ffinanceestate%2Fart%2F20170524%2F20031507&d=EkSOzQ7ZVjnG5t8dBASUilKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=997545cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Ffinanceestate%2Fart%2F20170524%2F20031507&h=d5832e8f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/20170524/20031507</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>3日前</strong><br />\n<br />\n另一大行消息說，目前情況與2013年不同，存款超標貸款選擇不多，任何銀行率先加按息等於「自殺」不做生意，倘滙豐加息，中銀「只會多謝」未必跟隨；除非明年港元拆息仍低企，資本成本增加壓力「捱足」一整個年度（今年僅半年影響）後，屆時加按息考慮才較逼切。<br />\n東亞銀行（023）總經理兼個人銀行處主管許文森昨出席新盤定息按揭計劃時表示，提高RWA下限對銀行資金成本帶來壓力，至於會否上調按息，則視乎各方面市況而定。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf07e2c115805f51f38da910ee2f49b50dde0449","tid":258976,"uid":53105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T05:38:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquo